  "title": "简单问题卡片的初始间隔应更大",
  "image_width": 1280,
  "content": "<p data-pid=\"O6SZNJ61\">对于特别简单的数学问题，比如 janich 的线性代数<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/index.php%3Ftitle%3DMultiple_choice_question%26action%3Dedit%26redlink%3D1\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">选择题</a>，可以设立单独一个牌组，其<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/index.php%3Ftitle%3DGraduating_interval%26action%3Dedit%26redlink%3D1\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">毕业间隔</a>设为一两年，所以我之后还能再看到几次。但毕业间隔够长，展示次数也不会频繁得让人烦躁。</p><p data-pid=\"S1Pp-vR4\">我觉得这样一来，十年之内的复习次数大概能减半。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><blockquote data-pid=\"Wv5nqeCB\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a> 汉化组译制<br/>题图 by Ara_Kieda<br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/wiki/Add_easy_problems_as_cards_with_large_graduating_interval\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Add easy problems as cards with large graduating interval</a></blockquote>",
